{"tid":1980210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情二字就是匪語","createTime":"2020-04-20T02:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T03:59:43.000Z","uid":268942,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2b59610e6f5ade29d6e995bcffcc9fd1ded40cef","tid":1980210,"uid":268942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:54:20.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報今日有版文字,評論匪語侵蝕香港問題。各位有無留意,武漢肺炎不許稱瘟疫而叫&quot;疫情&quot;,就是最氾濫的匪語。&quot;瘟疫&quot;兩字怵目驚心令人警覺,更讓人想起政權的邪惡。而&quot;疫情&quot;二字就起到緩衝,淡化的作用。就如某國人失業不叫失業稱&quot;待業&quot;,把炒魷叫做&quot;下崗&quot;一樣,時時刻刻在麻痺人民。"},{"pid":"c84ac13f11914f10cb7bec8e6a6227c0dfb199fe","tid":1980210,"uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T03:13:39.000Z","msg":"疫情個「疫」咪指瘟疫囉<br />\n<br />\n《集韻》&middot;平聲&middot;魂韻：「瘟，疫也。」"},{"pid":"b7eb24a5f41679a7ff5756e52091921684c62440","tid":1980210,"uid":316459,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T03:16:11.000Z","msg":"其實疫情全寫係瘟疫情況"},{"pid":"383ab1ebaba71a658e7ac582394d89f02933e973","tid":1980210,"uid":316459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T03:16:21.000Z","msg":"其實疫情全寫係瘟疫情況"},{"pid":"06f4d05ef35e8468300cc2e6484620579125325c","tid":1980210,"uid":87334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T03:27:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武漢肺炎</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武漢肺炎</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武漢肺炎</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武漢肺炎</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武漢肺炎</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武漢肺炎</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咪撚再講疫情淡化「武漢肺炎」！<br />\n <br />\n<strong><